casebody.data:
Friday, January 8, 1993

MOTION DOCKET

92-480. Burgess v. Eli Lilly & Co.

Certified Question of State Law. This matter is pending before the court on the certification of a state law question from the United States District Court for the Sixth Judicial Circuit. Upon consideration of respondent’s motion for Andrew See to appear pro hac vice,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion to appear pro hac vice be, and the same is hereby, granted.
